videoSnippet.description:

Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

David Janowski vs Jose Raul Capablanca
Rice Memorial (1916), New York, NY USA, rd 3, Feb-08 
Slav Defense: Three Knights Variation (D15)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 d5 3. c4 c6 4. Nc3 Bf5 5. Qb3 Qb6 6. Qb6 ab6 7. cd5 Nd5 8. Nd5 cd5 9. e3 Nc6 10. Bd2 Bd7 11. Be2 11 e6 12. O-O Bd6 13. Rfc1 Ke7 14. Bc3 Rhc8 15. a3 Na5 16. Nd2 f5 17. g3 b5 18. f3 Nc4 19. Bc4 bc4 20. e4 Kf7 21. e5 Be7 22. f4 b5 23. Kf2 Ra4 24. Ke3 Rca8 25. Rab1 h6 26. Nf3 g5 27. Ne1 Rg8 28. Kf3 gf4 29. gf4 Raa8 30. Ng2 Rg4 31. Rg1 Rag8 32. Be1 b4 33. ab4 Ba4 34. Ra1 Bc2 35. Bg3 Be4 36. Kf2 h5 37. Ra7 Bg2 38. Rg2 h4 39. Bh4 Rg2 40. Kf3 Rh2 41. Be7 Rh3 42. Kf2 Rb3 43. Bg5 Kg6 44. Re7 Rb2 45. Kf3 Ra8 46. Re6 Kh7
